name: email-templates
description: Skill dla tworzenia i testowania szablonów email
keywords:
  - templates
  - email
  - html
  - plaintext
  - rendering
topics:
  - templating
  - email
  - html
  - testing
applyTo:
  - path: "**/templates/**"
  - path: "**/*template*.py"
languageDetection:
  preferredLanguage: python
  patterns:
    - "template"
    - "html"
    - "jinja"
